data.description: SERIOUS BOATERS! Got a Go-fast or Cigarette boat? This is your new home! Check out the EXPANSIVE 3-way INTERSECTING Canal view from this GORGEOUSLY UPDATED & METICULOUSLY MAINTAINED western exposure salt water POOL HOME in the heart of Cape Coral IDEALLY LOCATED for QUICK ACCESS to some of the best fishing & boating in SW Florida! 27,000lb lift, Captain's Walk, concrete dock & davit accommodate multiple watercraft up to 38' & 15' beam. From your sparkling pool & paved deck, enjoy the LONG VIEW down a wide Gulf Access canal. IMMACULATE! NO Storm damage! Roof 2021; A/C 2019; impact windows. Lovely paved courtyard entry, fountain & custom front door welcome you into the SPACIOUS Great Room with STUNNING WATER VIEW & EXQUISITE attention to detail: custom-milled trim, baseboards & fireplace; crown molding; large neutral tile on diagonal; granite counters; high-end appliances; upgraded fixtures & hardware. TRUE Chef's Kitchen features built-in fridge, immense center island, soft-close drawers, solar tube, pantry & slide-out shelves. SO MANY EXTRAS . . . Custom closet cabinets, can lights w/dimmers, 3 laundry tubs; lushly landscaped fenced yard with walkways & outdoor rooms all around!
